creator: DJ Erycom Uganda
descriptionHtml:
About This App

Since 2007, DJ Erycom has been the biggest source for Uganda music. Most radio stations, DJs, promoters and other platforms rely on DJ Erycom for Uganda music.

In the year 2012 he launched www.djerycomcom a website that has turned into Uganda’s only Online Music Library.

This App together with our website www.djerycom.com offer you almost all Ugandan songs produced between 1960 to date.

In November 2018, this DJ Erycom App was launched so as to offer free, unlimited access to all new and old Ugandan songs of your choice.

Now, you can also watch Ugandan movies free from this DJ Erycom App


You Love DJ Erycom ?

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DJErycom
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DJErycom
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/DJ.Erycom

If you notice any song missing out on the DJ Erycom App, please contact our Promotions Team on whatsApp: +256752399999 or Email: erycom@djerycom.com
descriptionShort: Source Of New & Old Ugandan Music
